Više informacija o našoj ponudi možete videti na sajtu <a href="https://www.siguraplam.rs/">www.siguraplam.rs</a>.<br>Zadovoljstvo nam je da predstavimo proizvode koji do sada nisu bili zastupljeni u našoj ponudi – ormarića za prvu pomoć, čime je kompletirana naša ponuda iz oblasti preventive, sigurnosti i zaštite na radu.</p></div></div></div></div><div class="elementor-column elementor-col-50 elementor-inner-column elementor-element elementor-element-7c7e045a" data-id="7c7e045a" data-element_type="column"><div class="elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated"><div class="elementor-element elementor-element-4855ab0 elementor-align-center elementor-widget elementor-widget-lottie" data-id="4855ab0" data-element_type="widget" data-settings="{"source_json":{"url":"https:\/\/zidneapoteke.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/67986-business-deal.json","id":130,"size":"","alt":"","source":"library"},"reverse_animation":"yes","lazyload":"yes","source":"media_file","caption_source":"none","link_to":"none","trigger":"arriving_to_viewport","viewport":{"unit":"%","size":"","sizes":{"start":0,"end":100}},"play_speed":{"unit":"px","size":1,"sizes":[]},"start_point":{"unit":"%","size":"0","sizes":[]},"end_point":{"unit":"%","size":"100","sizes":[]},"renderer":"svg"}" data-widget_type="lottie.default"><div class="elementor-widget-container"><style>
